2000 until November 2001, Mr.&nbsp;Dalzell was Senior Vice
President and Chief Information Officer and prior to that, from
joining Amazon.com in August 1997 until October 2000, he was
Vice President and Chief Information Officer.
</FONT>

<P align="left">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
