General Electric Co., including Chief Financial Officer of GE
Lighting from September 2001 to September 2002, Finance Director
of GE Plastics Europe from March 1999 to September 2001, and
Executive Vice President&nbsp;&#151; Finance of GE Asset
Management (formerly known as GE Investments) from May 1997 to
March 1999.
