<FONT size="2">Based upon quoted market prices, the fair value
of the 4.75% Convertible Subordinated Notes as of
December&nbsp;31, 2002 and December&nbsp;31, 2001 was
$925&nbsp;million and $625&nbsp;million, respectively.
